com.glavsoft.rfb

Class RfbCapabilityInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.glavsoft.rfb.RfbCapabilityInfo

  • public class RfbCapabilityInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Structure used to describe protocol options such as tunneling methods, authentication schemes and message types (protocol versions 3.7t, 3.8t). typedef struct _rfbCapabilityInfo { CARD32 code; // numeric identifier CARD8 vendorSignature[4]; // vendor identification CARD8 nameSignature[8]; // abbreviated option name } rfbCapabilityInfo;
